{"tid":1586280,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[支持警察] 一齊重溫槍袋構造，防止暴徒搶槍","createTime":"2019-09-22T01:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T09:24:39.000Z","uid":123933,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8a728817876f6b054413aa907bb30779608af1d8","tid":1586280,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/ftp/News/20140916/HK/_16ga202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Ftor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20140916%2FHK%2F_16ga202.jpg&h=e412619a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1279019/org/441aad1068a7bd4b8ce62f82269dde3e.jpeg/uUb1KVofX5HiPDaOIDD5r0jpjH1OVFfeKphEKSqYRCk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1279019%2Forg%2F441aad1068a7bd4b8ce62f82269dde3e.jpeg%2FuUb1KVofX5HiPDaOIDD5r0jpjH1OVFfeKphEKSqYRCk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f84f6c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<strong><ins>拔槍時​需將將槍推前</ins></strong><br />\n當警員<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拔槍時，需先握槍柄，用拇指逼開頂部活動皮扣鈕扣，再將槍推前，壓緊槍身令鐵片鬆開，可拔出佩槍</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\nM-10佩槍雖無保險掣，惟必須將扳機拉到最低才能發射，是防止走火及胡亂開槍的安全裝置</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>警務人員現時使用中的槍袋有防搶設計，槍袋內最深處有如彈弓般的裝置扣着手槍，「直接拉支槍出嚟係拉唔到」，人員要拔槍，需有「二步曲」，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一步是要解開槍袋的「啪鈕」，第二步是要把手槍壓前，才可把槍取出。 </span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝明報同01同我地一班伙記重運學堂教過嘅野，下次記得小心，唔好再俾班暴徒有機可乘啦知無<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa9f025a755130246caa69b0d5456260c94158f","tid":1586280,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T01:20:01.000Z","msg":"支持ivan"},